title: Episode 177: Gigi Crazy (Feat. DJ Whoo Kid & LaBritney)
itunes:title: Episode 177: Gigi Crazy (Feat. DJ Whoo Kid & LaBritney)
description:
DJ Whoo Kid and Rapper LaBritney join the ladies of Lip Service this week and things get crazy when Whoo Kid reveals he takes pictures and videos with all celebrity partners he's been with. LaBritney admits she would redo the time she lost her virginity, Whoo Kid is relentless in calling Gigi crazy, and much more. Enjoy!
